  "text": "Recently, in Cano et al. [CITATION_1] , we demonstrated that exploiting the semantic information about entities from DBpedia and Freebase is beneficial. In particular, incorporating additional semantic information about entities in terms of properties and concepts can further improve the performance of a topic classifier against the approach using Twitter data only.",
